7:
Thank you, thank you! I love you
guys!
19:
Why do you insist on wielding the
light for deception?
21:
It is a power meant to cleave
through the darkness—to
counteract calamity and misfortune.
22:
Yet you continue to use it to serve
lies.
27:
I'm an illusionist, and I show people
the dreams they want to see!
Simple as that!
30:
You are guiding people to ruin...
Don't think the Guild won't hear
about this!
40:
He was saying the same stuff my
teacher used to...
48:
I need it... and only you can provide
for us!
66: Come on! Show me the magic!
68:
Me too! I've been searching for that
power all this time!
70:
Not sure what kinda crazy they're on,
but I can handle these small fries—
87:
Here comes Illumine's Show of
Spectacles!
94:
Oh my gosh, oh my gosh, oh my
gosh!
96: I can't hold back... Must... dance!
99:
Someone mind explainin' what the
heck is going on?
104:
Stella? Nimbus? You here for the
show too?
108: No, just... Who are these people?
114:
Guess you can call them my fans.
They've been to a whole bunch of
my shows before!
119:
When we saw her show back in the
boonies for the first time... we just
knew we'd have to make our own
debut in the city!
121:
But things didn't turn out so well for
us...
123:
We ended up homeless and living in
caves... which is why we've got a
favor to ask!
128:
I'm telling you, these guys reek of
trouble. The nose doesn't lie.
132:
Hehe, don't you worry about a thing!
I've got this!
141:
All right, folks. Your training begins
today, and it won't be easy! Get your
game faces on!
